#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

using ll = long long;
using VI = vector<ll>;

int main() {
  int t;
  cin >> t;
  while (t--) {
    int n;
    ll l;
    cin >> n >> l;
    vector<pair<ll, ll>> v(n);
    int k = 0;
    for (auto& i : v) {
      cin >> i.first;
      i.second = k++;
    }
    sort(v.begin(), v.end());
    VI res(n);

    bool ok = true;
    ll tot = 0, nex = 0;
    while (true) {
      int cv = v[nex].first;
      int ci = v[nex].second;
      if (v[nex].first != tot + 1) {
        ok = false;
        break;
      }
      ++res[ci];
      tot += cv;
      ++nex;
      if (nex < n) {
        if ((v[nex].first - 1 - tot) % cv != 0) {
          ok = false;
          break;
        }
        res[ci] += (v[nex].first - 1 - tot) / cv;
        tot = v[nex].first - 1;
      } else {
        if ((l - tot) % cv != 0) {
          ok = false;
          break;
        }
        res[ci] += (l - tot) / cv;
        break;
      }
    }
    if (ok) {
      for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {
        if (i) cout << " ";
        cout << res[i];
      }
      cout << endl;
    } else cout << -1 << endl;
  }
}
